      <title>Citgo 的委内瑞拉母公司称美国破产将导致销售放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/citgo-s-venezuelan-parent-said-to-weigh-bankruptcy-to-slow-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，委内瑞拉反对派正在考虑采取一项举措，通过让 Citgo Petroleum Corp. 的控股公司在美国申请破产来减缓其控制下的石油资产的出售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/citgo-s-venezuelan-parent-said-to-weigh-bankruptcy-to-slow-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 17:12:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党将大型石油调查送交司法部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/big-oil-investigation-sent-to-justice-department-by-democrats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会调查的结论是，指控大型石油公司数十年来在气候变化的影响方面欺骗公众，民主党人要求司法部对主要石油公司及其贸易团体进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/big-oil-investigation-sent-to-justice-department-by-democrats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 16:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
