    <item>
      <title>苏纳克在 7 月 4 日选举中赌博，保守党在民意调查中陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/uk-general-election-will-be-held-on-july-4-bbc-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 宣布英国将于 7 月 4 日举行大选，这是一场比预期提前投票的重大赌博，因为他领导的保守党在民意调查中远远落后于基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 领导的反对党工党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/uk-general-election-will-be-held-on-july-4-bbc-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 15:32:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
